Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節大作戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有各種各樣的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.57,0:02:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都想嘗一嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.88,0:02:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.83,0:02:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請吃我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.49,0:02:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的也務必
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝...謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年結果也沒送到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只好自己全吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天交換友情巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.88,0:02:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們準備做哪種？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時保密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與小誠同班 叫做西園寺茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 小誠的...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見到你真的很榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 有些事想要和姐姐大人稍微咨詢一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 那我們先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要咨詢什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 其實我啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想將來成為小誠的新娘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:40.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這樣啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 明天是很重要的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要用巧克力將小誠HeartCatch（的心俘獲）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節一年才一次 絕對不想失敗！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.43,0:04:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這次 我從法國請了巧克力大師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從 法國!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被教導 為了目的可以不惜金錢與船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花錢還能理解 這船...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我家奶媽 哦哈哈哈 （是個冷笑話...）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 奶媽啊 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 不知道小誠喜歡哪種巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐大人請務必告知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 小誠喜歡的是附近煙紙店的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之越甜越好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.65,0:04:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且能吃一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,量大到 每次都被媽媽訓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是萬分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會作為參考 作出巧克力送給小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.76,0:04:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜啊 是個雷厲風行的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.58,0:05:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很積極
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:17.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年才一次的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼小的孩子都這麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也不能落後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人節...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力敞開了吃的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃 要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 稍微有點不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.88,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡單說 情人節就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘以巧克力為禮物 送給所中意男性的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 以巧克力傳遞戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 巧克力能幫助戀愛 真是浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LianAi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LianAi是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛那是伴著組曲節拍的舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然也有獨自起舞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但兩人的話 便能編織為美妙的華爾茲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 小鬼頭是不會懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近幾年漸漸成為大家都可以享受 類似祭典的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟朋友、親人也交換禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽起來好有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想玩祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天家裡沒人 大家一起來做巧克力吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 果然我被踢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有妹子才能做巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.83,0:06:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻是料理師傅 所以特例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只管吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:06:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只管吃...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只管吃!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直好運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先做棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.49,0:07:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得好吃 咕嚕咕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.81,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吞撻吞撻 咕嚕咕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得好吃 咕嚕咕嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著要點綴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就是大家期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晃晃時間
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草莓棉花糖加上巧克粒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接著只需搖一搖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得好吃 我晃我晃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來試試各種各樣的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.55,0:08:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙子棉花糖加上曲奇 味道像是馬德琳（貝殼）蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這個猶如初戀的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 初戀的味道？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,草莓棉花糖加上檸檬汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又酸又甜的 正是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也給心彩做了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來嘗嘗看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直就是在吃草
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜瓜棉花糖加上了海帶汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可樂拌味噌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍色夏威夷加激辣咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.81,0:09:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也該做最後的點綴了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 要變得好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的巧克力也做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 看起來還真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個和另一邊的完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力分為本命與友情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啥區別
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊量產的是友情巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這邊的就是本命巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是要給心上人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心上人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.96,0:10:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴我 絕對會保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜雪兒絕對守不住秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 並不是說喜歡一之瀨同學什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.56,0:10:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個啊 一之瀨同學是學校排名第一的足球小帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前幫過我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以這是回禮 回禮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當成是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 能夠接受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼要怎麼送給他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 沒有正面送的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是放鞋箱裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做吧 做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧 上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠喜歡就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.73,0:10:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為妹子代表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來為心彩的情人節加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:10:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 要乖一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.08,0:11:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家想的都一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 受歡迎的就是不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.52,0:11:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有點自尊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我毫無自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 勉強成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到了友情巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想馬上就吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.94,0:12:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下我的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學真是人氣角色
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.86,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女生們的熱情也真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.89,0:12:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 雖然是盡心盡力做的 但感覺沒什麼自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在心彩的巧克力上施了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.55,0:12:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了就會隨著旋律哈↗皮↗皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著旋律哈↗皮↗皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這上也施那個魔法看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦哦～ 我是心彩～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦～ 藍藍的天～ 白白的雲～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊～ 我是小學5年級～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體自己動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰來...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦啦～ 阻止我～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個施在了送給一之瀨的巧克力上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 更強勁 大概要強100倍的大魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,100倍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 一之瀨同學會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩也會困擾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美蘿莉的心意 我很開心 謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這魔法稍微有點強過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能偷偷取回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是教室裡一直都有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄準從手工教室回來的空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用最快速度回沒人的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從一之瀨的櫃子裡取回巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要取回魔法巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快 趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來把風
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.19,0:15:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學抱歉 擅自打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡交給身體小巧的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你們倆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨真是非常好學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 這毛巾裝飾在我的房間如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這麼快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬菈莉絲 莎莎 快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.50,0:15:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩的巧克力就在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬菈莉絲 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:15:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽菜送誰巧克力了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才飛奔了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.14,0:16:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 稍微有點事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的課結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去訓練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣啊 要用櫃子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姬菈莉絲 躲好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好擔心姬菈莉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是在說『我來想辦法』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一個人不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩去分散他們的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:05.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來拿魔法巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分散他們的注意力 要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個請自己想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.95,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 試試最近掌握的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾位稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.44,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來見識一下我的翻花繩技術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡這樣 那裡那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘 足球球門完成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.31,0:17:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒興趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼還有什麼其他的花樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 還有 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 四葉 莫非你也要送一之瀨巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.53,0:17:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:18:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說 送我是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.75,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是送我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然收下完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.97,0:18:07.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔壁學校的女生都在校門口排隊等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.34,0:18:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們先練起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法巧克力就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是別做危險的舉動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 取回魔法巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搬不動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 被什麼卡住了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.16,0:19:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我也想要巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都找不到機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四葉誠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收下我的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.14,0:19:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}誒 不喜歡巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.54,0:19:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}不 是很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3}喜歡啊 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜 好勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,證明很看重小誠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定了 不用偷偷的去取回巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接跟一之瀨同學說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.41,0:20:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿回巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會很順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也為你加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.18,0:20:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.94,0:20:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 我在一之瀨的鞋櫃裡放了巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 能還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些搞錯了 都因為我笨手笨腳的 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.09,0:20:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最上面那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.68,0:20:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 作為補償 收下這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是友情巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也是用心做的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒的好味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.36,0:21:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是就這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個心驚肉跳 忐忑不安的美妙情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好呢 心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了 大家也來吃巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 心彩在做巧克力的時候 試吃過各種搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.14,0:22:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味覺被攪亂了 嘗不准正確的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.31,0:22:13.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好辣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.69,0:22:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的愛心蛋占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的幸運蛋是哪個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選中我的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃到好吃的零食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在公園發現了愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.35,0:24:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是三個
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公園的遊樂設施上誕生的愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.96,0:24:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱流浪蛋三連星
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.07,0:24:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是有點討厭人類的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.73,0:24:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家吵架 把人從公園趕跑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.08,0:24:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒 跟他們一決勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.59,0:24:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.04,0:24:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有來公園散步的老爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.19,0:24:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家和睦相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集『流浪蛋三連星 前來拜訪!』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.57,0:00:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說過世間萬物都有著靈魂 這樣的說法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼 只要被珍惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見習神仙愛心蛋 就會從中誕生哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是秘密事項喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:21.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 與大家來相見！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:24.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了…小神仙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.42,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:30.59,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.88,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好想要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:37.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（但但但是 不可以啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是有點被察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（這這這啊 最重要了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:52.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能說的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,要～怎麼辦啊～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:59.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 最愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 最愛你了 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:05.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 和睦友好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 你叫什麼呢?）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,真心的珍惜 世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:17.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來 最愛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.22,0:01:19.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 最愛你了 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:23.22,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋嘰裡咕嚕滾下來　永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:25.98,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（嗨嗨 看著我嘛 嗨嗨）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,勇敢的心兒永不言敗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.86,0:01:34.90,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,將有趣的夢想化為現實 一起來玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,砰砰敲出了…小神仙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:40.91,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,實現吧 大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.75,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}實現？個蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.11,0:22:30.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(330,0)}好運？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:35.62,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,乓乓乓 乓乓乓 乓乓乓!（嗨!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.29,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,乓乓乓 乓乓乓 乓乓乓!（咦…?）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:40.63,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}乓乓乓 乓乓乓！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.21,0:22:44.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,七色繽紛的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.98,0:22:47.44,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（扣扣塔嘛! 扣扣塔嘛!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:50.15,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,美美的閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.15,0:22:51.36,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（扣扣塔嘛!）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:56.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你真心的愛著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.78,0:23:02.66,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,想為你而實現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:05.45,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,（吶吶一起來、唱吧!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:10.83,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 扣扣塔嘛!（哇!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.83,0:23:12.96,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,在蛋殼裡藏著許許多多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.96,0:23:15.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,的夢·想（嗨! 嗨!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:18.05,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 扣扣塔嘛!（哇!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.22,0:23:20.97,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,尾巴甩甩 實現的話!（哇!）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:25.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,心兒也有會大大的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:29.73,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,NICO NICO的咪咪笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:43.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(206,666)}啊 啊… 一直要在一起!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:43.95,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1066,616)}（乓乓乓 乓乓乓 乓乓乓!）
